  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Defining Application Structure**\n\nOkay, I\'m deep diving into the application\'s structure. I am outlining the React components, considering how to organize them logically based on the HTML provided. It\'s becoming clearer how the UI elements will map to component hierarchies.\n\n\n**Analyzing Image Integration**\n\nI\'m now zeroing in on image handling, recognizing its importance given the placeholder URLs in the HTML. Image generation seems relevant. I will maintain the existing URLs, or, if necessary, develop a means to browse and present the images. The goal is to accurately represent the visual design.\n\n\n**Reviewing Multi-Screen Designs**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the multi-screen designs. Examining the product detail (Screen 1) with size selection and add-to-cart, alongside the Editorial home (Screen 2), and the jewelry brand screens (Screens 3 and 4), I begin to see the application\'s comprehensive scope. I am assessing how these diverse presentations can be integrated effectively into a cohesive user flow.\n\n\n**Mapping E-Commerce Flow**\n\nI\'m now integrating the e-commerce aspects, specifically focusing on the cart and product pages. I\'m taking into account the split sections, scrolling marquee, cart page with order details and \"VALIDER LA COMMANDE\" button, the category view, and the jewelry cart and catalogue with staggered grid designs. This includes diverse elements like price, quantity, filters, and image representation for each product category.\n\n\n**Integrating Category Displays**\n\nI\'m now focusing on integrating the category displays and product details for MYRIAM VEIL, specifically the e-commerce aspects of it. I\'m taking into account the product pages with price, materials and details, and the women\'s category page with the category filters and products. I\'ll need to figure out how to accurately render the models and information with the products, incorporating aspects such as the \"Explore The Collection\" button.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 7
      nanos: 822301752
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
